(25, 23, '[站长推荐]分享一个适合新手学习Git的地方', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">最近这段时间，在群里很多人再找学习Git的教程，小编也正在学习Git 找到几个不错的学习Git的网站，希望对大家有帮助。<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/><img src="http://i12.tietuku.com/dcb508cfaeddd777s.jpg" alt="git" data-bd-imgshare-binded="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: middle; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; background: transparent;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">首先我们来了解下什么是Git</p><blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 30px -24px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 24px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 6px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(81, 173, 237); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; quotes: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p>Git是一款免费、开源的分布式版本控制系统，用于敏捷高效地处理任何或小或大的项目。<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 0; position: relative; top: -0.5em; background: transparent;">[1]</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(234, 234, 234); font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: all 0.2s ease; color: rgb(81, 173, 237); background: transparent;" name="ref_[1]_12032478"></a>&nbsp; Git的读音为/gɪt/。</p><p>Git是一个开源的分布式版本控制系统，用以有效、高速的处理从很小到非常大的项目版本管理。<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 0; position: relative; top: -0.5em; background: transparent;">[2]</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(234, 234, 234); font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: all 0.2s ease; color: rgb(81, 173, 237); background: transparent;" name="ref_[2]_12032478"></a>&nbsp; Git 是 Linus Torvalds 为了帮助管理 Linux 内核开发而开发的一个开放源码的版本控制软件。</p><p>Torvalds 开始着手开发 Git 是为了作为一种过渡方案来替代 BitKeeper，后者之前一直是 Linux 内核开发人员在全球使用的主要源代码工具。开放源码社区中的有些人觉得 BitKeeper 的许可证并不适合开放源码社区的工作，因此 Torvalds 决定着手研究许可证更为灵活的版本控制系统。尽管最初 Git 的开发是为了辅助 Linux 内核开发的过程，但是我们已经发现在很多其他自由软件项目中也使用了 Git。例如 最近就迁移到 Git 上来了，很多 Freedesktop 的项目也迁移到了 Git 上。<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 0; position: relative; top: -0.5em; background: transparent;">[2]</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(234, 234, 234); font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: all 0.2s ease; color: rgb(81, 173, 237); background: transparent;" name="ref_[2]_12032478"></a></p></blockquote><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">实战学习Git的网站：<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">实验楼（<a href="https://www.shiyanlou.com/courses/?course_type=all&tag=Git" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="external" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(234, 234, 234); font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: all 0.2s ease; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(81, 173, 237); background: transparent;">点我进入</a>）</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这个网站，小编大概关注了一年多了吧~ 感觉还不错，是个学习的好地方，里面有各种各样的教程。有兴趣的朋友可以去看看。额~~跑题了。我这不是打广告哈。。。 &nbsp; 继续回来说 进去需要注册下，我是用的QQ授权登陆的，登陆后进去学习就可以了。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">再给大家推荐个使用Git的教程吧</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Git Community Book 中文版（<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><a href="http://gitbook.liuhui998.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="external" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(234, 234, 234); font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: all 0.2s ease; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(81, 173, 237); background: transparent;">点击进入</a></strong>）</p><p><br/></p>', '波仔', '2016-02-28 16:48:00', 'Git是一款免费、开源的分布式版本控制系统，用于敏捷高效地处理任何或小或大的项目。[1]  Git的读音为/gɪt/。\r\nGit是一个开源的分布式版本控制系统，用以有效、高速的处理从很小到非常大的项目版本管理。[2]  Git 是 Linus Torvalds 为了帮助管理 Linux 内核开发而开发的一个开放源码的版本控制软件。'),
(26, 28, '基于php设计模式中单例模式的应用分析', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">单例模式：简单的说，一个对象只负责一个特定的任务。</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/><img src="http://i13.tietuku.com/d382d1ced8b126abs.jpg" alt="php单例" data-bd-imgshare-binded="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: middle; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; background: transparent;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">单例类:<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.构造函数需要标记为private，单例类不能再其他类中实例化，只能被其自身实例化<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>2.拥有一个保存类的实例静态成员变量<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>3.拥有一个访问这个实例的公共的静态方法。[常用getInstance()方法进行实例化单例类，通过instanceof操作符可以检测到此类是否已经被实例化]<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>注：需要创建__clone()方法防治对象被复制<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">作用：<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.php的应用主要用于数据库，所以一个应用中会存在大量的数据库操作，使用单例模式，则可以避免大量new操作消耗的资源<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>2.如果系统中需要一个类来全局控制某些配置信息，那么使用单例模式可以很方便的实现。参照ZF的FrontController部分<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>3.在一个页面请求汇总，便于进行调试，因为所有的代码都集中在一个类中，我们可以在类中设置钩子，输出日志，从而避免到处var_dump，echo。</p><p><a id="copybut14159" class="copybut" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(234, 234, 234); font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: all 0.2s ease; color: rgb(81, 173, 237); background: transparent;"></a><span style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;text-decoration:underline;">复制代码</span>&nbsp;代码如下:</p><p>class DanLi{<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>//静态成员变量<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>private static $_instance;<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>//私有的构造方法<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>private function __construct(){<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>}<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>//防止对象被克隆<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>public function __clone(){<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>trigger_error(&#39;Clone is not allow!&#39;,E_USER_ERROR);<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>}<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>public static function getInstance(){<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>if(!(self::$_instance instanceof self)){<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>self::$_instance = new self;<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>}<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>return self::$_instance;<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>}<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>public function test(){<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>echo &quot;ok&quot;;<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>}<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>}</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">//错误：$danli = new DanLi(); $danli_clone = clone $danli;<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>//正确：$danli = DanLi::getInstance(); $danli-&gt;test();</p><p>?&gt;</p><p><br/></p>', '站长', '2016-02-28 16:51:00', '基于php设计模式中单例模式的应用分析'),
(27, 25, '深入分析php之面向对象', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">以前对面向对象仅限于死记硬背型，工作这么久了，回过头来看又是一翻体悟，供大家看看。<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/><img src="http://i13.tietuku.com/03904a39ce65ac3es.png" alt="深入分析php之面向对象" data-bd-imgshare-binded="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: middle; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; background: transparent;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">1.final<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/></strong>final：php5新增一个final关键字。如果父类中的方法被声明为final，则子类无法覆盖该方法；如果一个类被声明final，则不能被继承。</p><p><a id="copybut84473" class="copybut" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(234, 234, 234); font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: all 0.2s ease; color: rgb(81, 173, 237); background: transparent;"></a><span style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;text-decoration:underline;">复制代码</span>&nbsp;代码如下:</p><p>class BaseClass{<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>public function test(){<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>ehco &quot;test&quot;;<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>}final public function moreTest(){<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>echo &quot;moretest&quot;;<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>}<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>}</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">class ChildClass extends BaseClass{<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>public function moreTest(){<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>echo &quot;moretest&quot;;<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>}<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>}<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>// 产生 Fatal error: Cannot override final method BaseClass::moretest()</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border