background: transparent;">else</code>&nbsp;<code class="plain" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">{</code></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;" class="firstRow"><td class="number" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">9</code></td><td class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 0px 350px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; float: left; max-width: 820px; background: transparent;" width="NaN"><code class="spaces" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class="plain" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">parent::display(</code><code class="variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">$templateFile</code><code class="plain" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">,</code><code class="variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">$charset</code><code class="plain" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">,</code><code class="variable" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">$contentType</code><code class="plain" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">);</code></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;" class="firstRow"><td class="number" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">10</code></td><td class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 0px 350px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; float: left; max-width: 820px; background: transparent;" width="NaN"><code class="spaces" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class="plain" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">}</code></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;" class="firstRow"><td class="number" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">11</code></td><td class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 0px 350px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; float: left; max-width: 820px; background: transparent;" width="NaN"><code class="plain" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">}</code></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br/></p>', 'bobo', '2016-02-28 16:01:00', '首先带大家了解下开启gzip的好处：\r\ngzip顾名思义就是网站压缩。压缩网站有哪些好处呢，加快访客的访问速度,节省服务器带宽，从而达到带宽小能多承载用户，测试了一下,基本大网站都开启了gizp。那gizp会不会对你网站的收录有影响呢，答案是GZIP压缩的网页对搜索引擎是友好的。既然开启gzip有这么多好处，那么我们应该怎样开启gzip呢?'),
(30, 27, 'thinkphp3.2.2升级3.2.3后 Base table or view not found: 1146解决办法', '<p>thinkphp3.2.2升级3.2.3后 Base table or view not found: 1146解决办法</p><p>在没升级前如果thinkphp中没有对应的数据表，直接定义模型就可以了，用D方法实例化就可以了，不过最近tp升级到3.2.3后出现问题提示错误：SQLSTATE[42S02]: Base table or view not found: 1146 Table ‘gudong365.gd_weixin’ doesn’t exist &nbsp;我确实没有创建gd_weixin这张表，但是模型是这样定义的：WeixinModel</p><p><br/></p><p>搜索了下官方网站，也有人问过这个问题，官方这样回复：【关闭调试模式应该就没有了，模型类没有对应的数据表的话 最好设置为虚拟模型】这样的回答对我这样的小白来说模棱两可，关闭调试模式是很好关闭，最好设置为虚拟模型，幸好还有手册，搜索了下：原来有这个虚拟模型，以前根本木有用过……</p><p><br/></p><p>虚拟模型是指虽然是模型类，但并不会真正的操作数据库的模型。有些时候，我们建立模型类但又不需要进行数据库操作，仅仅是借助模型类来封装一些业务逻辑，那么可以借助虚拟模型来完成。虚拟模型不会自动连接数据库，因此也不会自动检测数据表和字段信息，有两种方式可以定义虚拟模型：</p><p><br/></p><p>所以如果定义的模型没有对应的数据表，只要这样就搞定了：</p><p><br/></p><p>protected $autoCheckFields =false; &nbsp;（这里就是官方说的【最好设置为虚拟模型】）</p><p><br/></p><p>这样的话就运行成功啦。麻烦官方回复的时候直接一点…… &nbsp;也好考虑下我们这些小白的感受。</p><p><br/></p>', '波仔', '2016-02-28 16:48:00', '搜索了下官方网站，也有人问过这个问题，官方这样回复：【关闭调试模式应该就没有了，模型类没有对应的数据表的话 最好设置为虚拟模型】这样的回答对我这样的小白来说模棱两可，关闭调试模式是很好关闭，最好设置为虚拟模型，幸好还有手册，搜索了下：原来有这个虚拟模型，以前根本木有用过……');
INSERT INTO `web_article` (`web_artid`, `web_claid`, `web_title`, `web_text`, `web_author`, `web_time`, `web_introduce`) VALUES
(31, 28, '在ubtntu下操作mysql的删除与安装', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://i11.tietuku.com/57110442db412172s.png" alt="在ubtntu下操作mysql的删除与安装" data-bd-imgshare-binded="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: middle; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; background: transparent;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">删除mysql</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">sudo apt-get autoremove --purge mysql-server-5.0</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">sudo apt-get remove mysql-server</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">sudo apt-get autoremove mysql-server</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">sudo apt-get remove mysql-common</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">清理残留数据</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">dpkg -l |grep ^rc|awk &#39;{print $2}&#39; |sudo xargs dpkg -p</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">安装mysql</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">sudo apt-get install mysql-server</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">sudo apt-get install mysql-client</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">sudo apt-get install php5-mysql</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一旦安装完成，mysql服务器就会自动启动</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">执行命令sudo netstat -tap | grep mysql出现tcp 0 0 localhost.localdomain:mysql *:* LISTEN -</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">如果服务器不能正常运行，输入命令sudo /etc/init.d/mysql restart</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">进入mysql $mysql -u root -p(password)</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">配置mysql管理员密码</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">sudo mysqladmin -u root password newpassword</p><p><br/></p>', '站长', '2016-02-28 17:48:00', '\r\n删除mysql\r\n\r\nsudo apt-get autoremove --purge mysql-server-5.0\r\n\r\nsudo apt-get remove mysql-server\r\n\r\nsudo apt-get autoremove mysql-server'),
(32, 26, 'Mysql的基本操作（新手必看哟）', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">应很多网友的需求，以下是小编为大家总结的 希望对大家会有一些帮助，都是一些简单的命令，大牛可以直接略过。。。 好了废话不多说了 看正文</p><ol style="list-style-type: square;" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>创建数据库</p></li></ol><p class="NewStyle15" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　　　　　create&nbsp;database&nbsp;数据库名字</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　２．显示所有数据库</p><p class="NewStyle15" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　　　　　show&nbsp;databases;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　３．显示所有表：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">use&nbsp;&nbsp;数据库名字</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">show&nbsp;tables;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">4．显示所有表结构</p><p class="NewStyle15" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　　　　Desc&nbsp;table;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　5．显示所有存储过程</p><p class="NewStyle15" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　　　　show&nbsp;procedure&nbsp;status;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　６．显示创建存储过程的详情</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">show&nbsp;create&nbsp;procedure&nbsp;sp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">７．删除存储过程</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">drop&nbsp;procedure&nbsp;if&nbsp;exists&nbsp;sp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">８．删除数据库</p><p class="NewStyle15" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　　　　drop&nbsp;database;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　９．创建表主键自增</p><p class="NewStyle15" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">　　　　　create&nbsp;table&nbsp;user(<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>userid&nbsp;int(4)&nbsp;primary&nbsp;key&nbsp;not&nbsp;null&nbsp;auto_increment,<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>username&nbsp;varchar(16)&nbsp;not&nbsp;null,<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/>userpassword&nbsp;varchar(32)&nbsp;not&nbsp;null);</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p>', 'admin', '2016-02-28 16:34:00', 'Mysql的基本操作（新手必看哟）');
INSERT INTO `web_article` (`web_artid`, `web_claid`, `web_title`, `web_text`, `web_author`, `web_time`, `web_introduce`) VALUES
(33, 28, 'Linux(centos)系统各个目录的作用详解', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">文件系统的类型<br style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;"/><img src="http://i11.tietuku.com/5ca00becdad4cccds.png" alt="linux目录详解" data-bd-imgshare-binded="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: middle; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; background: transparent;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">LINUX有四种基本文件系统类型：普通文件、目录文件、连接文件和特殊文件，可用file命令来识别。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">普通文件：如文本文件、C语言元代码、SHELL脚本、二进制的可执行文件等，可用cat、less、more、vi、emacs来察看内容，用mv来改名。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">目录文件：包括文件名、子目录名及其指针。它是LINUX储存文件名的唯一地方，可用ls列出目录文件。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">连接文件：是指向同一索引节点的那些目录条目。用ls来查看是，连接文件的标志用l开头，而文件面后以&quot;-&gt;&quot;指向所连接的文件。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">特殊文件：LINUX的一些设备如磁盘、终端、打印机等都在文件系统中表示出来，则一类文件就是特殊文件，常放在/dev目录内。例如，软驱A称为/dev/fd0。LINUX无C：的概念，而是用/dev/had来自第一硬盘。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">对于linux新手来说，最感到迷惑的问题之一就是文件都存在哪里呢?特别是对于那些从windows转过来的新手来说，linux的目录结构看起来有些奇怪哦。所以，在这里讲一下linux下的主要目录以及它们都是用来干什么的。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">This is the root directory. The mothership. The home field. The one and only top directory for your whole computer. Everything, and I mean EVERYTHING starts here. When you type ‘/home’ what you’re really saying is “start at / and then go to the home directory.”</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这就是根目录。对你的电脑来说，有且只有一个根目录。所有的东西，我是说所有的东西都是从这里开始。举个例子：当你在终端里输入“/home”，你其实是在告诉电脑，先从/(根目录)开始，再进入到home目录。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/root</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">This is where the root user lives. The root user is the god of your system. Root can do anything, up to and including removing your entire filesystem. So be careful using root.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/root</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这是系统管理员(root user)的目录。对于系统来说，系统管理员就好比是上帝，它能对系统做任何事情，甚至包括删除你的文件。因此，请小心使用root帐号。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/bin</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Here’s where your standard linux utilities(read programs) live — things like “ls” and “vi” and “more”. Generally this directory is included in your path. What this means is that if you type ‘ls’, /bin is one of the places your shell will look to see if ‘ls’ means anything.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/bin</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这里存放了标准的(或者说是缺省的)linux的工具，比如像“ls”、“vi”还有“more”等等。通常来说，这个目录已经包含在你的“path”系 统变量里面了。什么意思呢?就是：当你在终端里输入ls，系统就会去/bin目录下面查找是不是有ls这个程序。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/etc</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Here’s where the administrative and system configuration stuff lives. For instance, if you have samba installed, and you want to modify the samba configuration files, you’d find them in /etc/samba.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/etc</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这里主要存放了系统配置方面的文件。举个例子：你安装了samba这个套件，当你想要修改samba配置文件的时候，你会发现它们(配置文件)就在/etc/samba目录下。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/dev</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Here’s where files that control peripherals live. Talking to a printer? Your computer is doing it from here. Same goes for disk drives, usb devices, and other such stuff.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/dev</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这里主要存放与设备(包括外设)有关的文件(unix和linux系统均把设备当成文件)。想连线打印机吗?系统就是从这个目录开始工作的。另外还有一些包括磁盘驱动、USB驱动等都放在这个目录。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/home</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Here’s where your data is stored. Config files specific to users, your Desktop folder(whick makes your desktop what it is), and any data related to your user. Each user will have their own /home/username folder, with the exception of the root user.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/home</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这里主要存放你的个人数据。具体每个用户的设置文件，用户的桌面文件夹，还有用户的数据都放在这里。每个用户都有自己的用户目录，位置为：/home/用户名。当然，root用户除外。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/tmp</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">This is the Temporary folder. Think of it as a scratch directory for your Linux system. Files that won’t be needed by programs once their used once or twice are put here. Many Linux systems are set to automatically wipe the /tmp folder at certain intervals, so don’t put things you want to keep here.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/tmp</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这是临时目录。对于某些程序来说，有些文件被用了一次两次之后，就不会再被用到，像这样的文件就放在这里。有些linux系统会定期自动对这个目录进行清理，因此，千万不要把重要的数据放在这里。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/usr</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Here’s where you’ll find extra utilities that don’t fit under /bin or /etc. Things like games, printer utilities, and whatnot. /usr is divided into sections like /usr/bin for programs, /usr/share for shared data like sound files or icons, /usr/lib for libraries whick cannot be directly run but are essential for running other programs.Your package manager takes care of the things in /usr for you.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/usr</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在这个目录下，你可以找到那些不适合放在/bin或/etc目录下的额外的工具。比如像游戏阿，一些打印工具拉等等。/usr目录包含了许多子目录： /usr/bin目录用于存放程序;/usr/share用于存放一些共享的数据，比如音乐文件或者图标等等;/usr/lib目录用于存放那些不能直接 运行的，但却是许多程序运行所必需的一些函数库文件。你的软件包管理器(应该是“新立得”吧)会自动帮你管理好/usr目录的。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/opt</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Here’s where optional stuff is put. Trying out the latest Firefox beta? Install it to /opt where you can delete it without affecting other settings. Programs in here usually live inside a single folder whick contains all of their data, libraries, etc.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/opt</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这里主要存放那些可选的程序。你想尝试最新的firefox测试版吗?那就装到/opt目录下吧，这样，当你尝试完，想删掉firefox的时候，你就可 以直接删除它，而不影响系统其他任何设置。安装到/opt目录下的程序，它所有的数据、库文件等等都是放在同个目录下面。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">举个例子：刚才装的测试版firefox，就可以装到/opt/firefox_beta目录下，/opt/firefox_beta目录下面就包含了运 行firefox所需要的所有文件、库、数据等等。要删除firefox的时候，你只需删除/opt/firefox_beta目录即可，非常简单。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/usr/local</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">This is where most manually installed(ie. outside of your package manager) software goes. It has the same structure as /usr. It is a good idea to leave /usr to your package manager and put any custom scripts and things into /usr/local, since nothing important normally lives in /usr/local.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/usr/local</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这里主要存放那些手动安装的软件，即不是通过“新立得”或apt-get安装的软件。它和/usr目录具有相类似的目录结构。让软件包管理器来管理/usr目录，而把自定义的脚本(scripts)放到/usr/local目录下面，我想这应该是个不错的主意。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/media</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Some distros use this folder to mount things like usb disks, cd or dvd drives and other filesystems.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/media</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">有些linux的发行版使用这个目录来挂载那些usb接口的移动硬盘(包括U盘)、CD/DVD驱动器等等。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">补充：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/bin 系统所需要的那些命令位于此目录，比如 ls、cp、mkdir等命令;功能和/usr/bin类似，这个目录中的文件都是可执行的、普通用户都可以使用的命令。作为基础系统所需要的最基础的命令就是放在这里(/usr/bin和/usr/sbin 类似与“/”根目录下对应的目录(/bin和/sbin)，但不用于基本的启动(譬如，在紧急维护中)。大多数命令在这个目录下。 )。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/boot Linux的内核及引导系统程序所需要的文件目录，比如 vmlinuz initrd.img 文件都位于这个目录中。在一般情况下，GRUB或LILO系统引导管理器也位于这个目录。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/lost+found 在ext2或ext3文件系统中，当系统意外崩溃或机器意外关机，而产生一些文件碎片放在这里。当系统启动的过程中fsck工具会检查这里，并修复已经损 坏的文件系统。 有时系统发生问题，有很多的文件被移到这个目录中，可能会用手工的方式来修复，或移到文件到原来的位置上。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/mnt 这个目录一般是用于存放挂载储存设备的挂载目录的，比如有cdrom 等目录。可以参看/etc/fstab的定义。有时我们可以把让系统开机自动挂载文件系统，把挂载点放在这里也是可以的。主要看/etc/fstab中怎 么定义了;比如光驱可以挂载到/mnt/cdrom 。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/opt 表示的是可选择的意思，有些软件包也会被安装在这里，也就是自定义软件包，比如在Fedora Core 5.0中，OpenOffice就是安装在这里。有些我们自己编译的软件包，就可以安装在这个目录中;通过源码包安装的软件，可以通过 ./configure --prefix=/opt/目录 。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/proc 操作系统运行时，进程信息及内核信息(比如cpu、硬盘分区、内存信息等)存放在这里。/proc目录伪装的文件系统proc的挂载目录，proc并不是真正的文件系统，它的定义可以参见 /etc/fstab 。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/sbin 大多是涉及系统管理的命令的存放，是超级权限用户root的可执行命令存放地，普通用户无权限执行这个目录下的命令，这个目录和/usr/sbin; /usr/X11R6/sbin或/usr/local/sbin目录是相似的;我们记住就行了，凡是目录sbin中包含的都是root权限才能执行的。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/usr 这个是系统存放程序的目录，比如命令、帮助文件等。这个目录下有很多的文件和目录。当我们安装一个Linux发行版官方提供的软件包时，大多安装在这里。 如果有涉及服务器配置文件的，会把配置文件安装在/etc目录中。/usr目录下包括涉及字体目录/usr/share/fonts ，帮助目录 /usr/share/man或/usr/share/doc，普通用户可执行文件目录/usr/bin 或/usr/local/bin 或/usr/X11R6/bin ，超级权限用户root的可执行命令存放目录，比如 /usr/sbin 或/usr/X11R6/sbin 或/usr/local/sbin 等;还有程序的头文件存放目录/usr/include。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/var 这个目录的内容是经常变动的，看名字就知道，我们可以理解为vary的缩写，/var下有/var/log 这是用来存放系统日志的目录。/var/www目录是定义Apache服务器站点存放目录;/var/lib 用来存放一些库文件，比如MySQL的，以及MySQL数据库的的存放地;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">关于/opt目录的一个小技巧</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在Linux中，/opt目录是存放某些大型软件或者某些特殊软件的目录，比如谷歌浏览器(Google Chrome)默认就是安装在/opt中。但是我们一般不会把opt单独分在一个区，因为/opt中大多数时候是空的，即使安装了软件也不会太多，而且有 些软件的容量还比较大，这样就会占用/的容量，我们可以在其它你愿意的地方建立一个目录来将/opt“转移”到别处，比如我的的/usr是单独分在一个 区，容量有50G，这么大的空间不要浪费了不是?而且/usr本来就是安装软件的地方，所以我可以/usr下建立一个叫opt的文件夹，然后右键点击这个 /usr下的opt，选择“创建链接”，得到一个名为“到 opt 的链接”文件，然后把这个文件剪切到/下，将原来的/opt删除，再将“到 opt 的链接”改名为opt就可以了，以后我们安装在/opt的软件实际上是安装到了/usr/opt下(实际上是一个符号链接)。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/usr/local 这个目录一般是用来存放用户自编译安装软件的存放目录;一般是通过源码包安装的软件，如果没有特别指定安装目录的话，一般是安装在这个目录中。这个目录下面有子目录。自己看看吧。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/usr/share 系统共用的东西存放地，比如 /usr/share/fonts 是字体目录，/usr/share/doc和/usr/share/man帮助文件。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/var/log 系统日志存放，分析日志要看这个目录的东西;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">/var/spool 打印机、邮件、代理服务器等假脱机目录;</p><p><br/></p>', '小飞', '2016-02-28 16:11:00', 'LINUX有四种基本文件系统类型：普通文件、目录文件、连接文件和特殊文件，可用file命令来识别。\r\n\r\n普通文件：如文本文件、C语言元代码、SHELL脚本、二进制的可执行文件等，可用cat、less、more、vi、emacs来察看内容，用mv来改名。\r\n\r\n目录文件：包括文件名、子目录名及其指针。它是LINUX储存文件名的唯一地方，可用ls列出目录文件。');
INSERT INTO `web_article` (`web_artid`, `web_claid`, `web_title`, `web_text`, `web_author`, `web_time`, `web_introduce`) VALUES
(34, 24, 'Linux下sftp配置之密钥方式登录', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">由于vsftp采用明文传输，用户名密码可通过抓包得到，为了安全性，需使用sftp，锁定目录且不允许sftp用户登到服务器。由于sftp使用的是ssh协议，需保证用户只能使用sftp，不能ssh到机器进行操作，且使用密钥登陆、不是22端口。</p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 15px 0px 15px -30px; padding: 5px 15px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(81, 173, 237); font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1. 创建sftp服务用户组,创建sftp服务根目录</h3><ol class="dp-py list-paddingleft-2" start="1" style="list-style-type: square;"><li><p>groupadd&nbsp;sftp</p></li></ol><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">#此目录及上级目录的所有者必须为root，权限不高于755，此目录的组最好设定为sftp</p><ol class="dp-py list-paddingleft-2" start="1" style="list-style-type: square;"><li><p>mkdir&nbsp;/data/sftp</p></li><li><p>chown&nbsp;-R&nbsp;root:sftp&nbsp;/data/sftp</p></li><li><p>chmod&nbsp;-R&nbsp;0755&nbsp;/data/sftp</p></li></ol><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 15px 0px 15px -30px; padding: 5px 15px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(81, 173, 237); font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2. 修改sshd配置文件</h3><ol class="dp-py list-paddingleft-2" start="1" style="list-style-type: square;"><li><p>cp&nbsp;/etc/ssh/sshd_config,_bk}&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">#备份配置文件</span></p></li><li><p>sed&nbsp;-i&nbsp;&#39;s@<span class="comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">#Port&nbsp;22@Port&nbsp;22@&#39;&nbsp;/etc/ssh/sshd_config&nbsp;&nbsp;#保证原来22端口可以</span></p></li><li><p>vi&nbsp;/etc/ssh/sshd_config</p></li></ol><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">注释掉/etc/ssh/sshd_config文件中的此行代码：</p><ol class="dp-py list-paddingleft-2" start="1" style="list-style-type: square;"><li><p>Subsystem&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sftp&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/usr/libexec/openssh/sftp-server</p></li></ol><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">添加如下代码：</p><ol class="dp-py list-paddingleft-2" start="1" style="list-style-type: square;"><li><p>Port&nbsp;2222</p></li><li><p>Subsystem&nbsp;sftp&nbsp;internal-sftp&nbsp;-l&nbsp;INFO&nbsp;-f&nbsp;AUTH</p></li><li><p>Match&nbsp;Group&nbsp;sftp</p></li><li><p>ChrootDirectory&nbsp;/data/sftp/%u</p></li><li><p>X11Forwarding&nbsp;no</p></li><li><p>AllowTcpForwarding&nbsp;no</p></li><li><p>ForceCommand&nbsp;internal-sftp&nbsp;-l&nbsp;INFO&nbsp;-f&nbsp;AUTH</p></li></ol><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">凡是在用户组sftp里的用户，都可以使用sftp服务；使用sftp服务连接上之后，可访问目录为/data/sftp/username</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">举个例子：</strong></p><blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 30px -24px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 24px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 6px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(81, 173, 237); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; quotes: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">test是一个sftp组的用户，它通过sftp连接服务器上之后，只能看到/data/sftp/test目录下的内容</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">test2也是一个sftp组的用户，它通过sftp连接服务器之后，只能看到/data/sftp/test2目录下的内容</p></blockquote><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 15px 0px 15px -30px; padding: 5px 15px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(81, 173, 237); font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">3. 创建sftp用户</h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">#此例将创建一个名称为test的sftp帐号</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">#创建test sftp家目录：test目录的所有者必须是root，组最好设定为sftp，权限不高于755</p><ol class="dp-py list-paddingleft-2" start="1" style="list-style-type: square;"><li><p>mkdir&nbsp;/data/sftp/test</p></li><li><p>chmod&nbsp;0755&nbsp;/data/sftp/test</p></li><li><p>chown&nbsp;root:sftp&nbsp;/data/sftp/test</p></li><li><p>useradd&nbsp;-g&nbsp;sftp&nbsp;-s&nbsp;/sbin/nologin&nbsp;test&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">#添加用户，参数-s&nbsp;/sbin/nologin禁止用户通过命令行登录</span></p></li></ol><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">创建test用户密钥对：</p><ol class="dp-py list-paddingleft-2" start="1" style="list-style-type: square;"><li><p><span class="comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">#&nbsp;mkdir&nbsp;/home/test/.ssh</span></p></li><li><p><span class="comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">#&nbsp;ssh-keygen&nbsp;-t&nbsp;rsa</span></p></li><li><p><span class="comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">#&nbsp;cp&nbsp;/root/.ssh/id_rsa.pub&nbsp;/home/test/.ssh/authorized_keys</span></p></li><li><p><span class="comment" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">#&nbsp;chown&nbsp;-R&nbsp;test.sftp&nbsp;/home/test</span></p></li></ol><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在test目录下创建一个可以写的upload目录</p><ol class="dp-py list-paddingleft-2" start="1" style="list-style-type: square;"><li><p>mkdir&nbsp;/data/sftp/test/upload</p></li><li><p>chown&nbsp;-R&nbsp;test:sftp&nbsp;/data/sftp/test/upload</p></li></ol><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">注：</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">sftp服务的根目录的所有者必须是root，权限不能超过755(上级目录也必须遵循此规则)，sftp的用户目录所有者也必须是root,且最高权限不能超过755。</strong></p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 15px 0px 15px -30px; padding: 5px 15px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(81, 173, 237); font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">4. 测试sftp</h3><ol class="dp-py list-paddingleft-2" start="1" style="list-style-type: square;"><li><p>service&nbsp;sshd&nbsp;restart</p></li></ol><p style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">test用户密钥登陆如下图：</p><p><img title="" src="https://blog.linuxeye.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/sftp_demo.png" alt="" data-bd-imgshare-binded="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: middle; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; background: transparent;"/></p><p><br/></p>', '波仔111', '2016-02-28 16:48:00', '由于vsftp采用明文传输，用户名密码可通过抓包得到，为了安全性，需使用sftp，锁定目录且不允许sftp用户登到服务器。由于sftp使用的是ssh协议，需保证用户只能使用sftp，不能ssh到机器进行操作，且使用密钥登陆、不是22端口。');

